19:51.540 --> 19:52.860
I don't think it's going to collapse.

19:52.860 --> 19:57.340
I think that it's going to change, and that change may well be for the worse, but I don't

19:57.340 --> 20:00.820
think it's just going to go away after 20-odd years of being around.

