24:44.620 --> 24:49.220
a button that has to be pressed with a retina ID authorization.

24:49.220 --> 24:54.660
It's more like our staff are just dispersed, we're kind of unproductive, so we'll just

24:54.660 --> 24:56.180
focus on security for now.

24:56.180 --> 24:57.180
Yeah, I think so.

24:57.180 --> 24:58.180
All right.

